services that they need to configure.

00:38:39.200 --> 00:38:42.870
You've got your DNS, your DHCP,
you've got your firewall,

00:38:42.870 --> 00:38:47.780
you might be running VPN,
you've got to set up port mapping, NAT.

00:38:47.780 --> 00:38:49.240
There's a lot of different services.

00:38:49.240 --> 00:38:51.330
So in Tiger Server,
one of the things we're making

00:38:51.330 --> 00:38:55.760
it much easier to do is set up,
easier to set up all these

00:38:55.760 --> 00:38:58.660
disparate different services.

